com.clxcommunications.xms

Class ApiHttpAsyncClient

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.clxcommunications.xms.ApiHttpAsyncClient
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Closeable, AutoCloseable, HttpAsyncClient

    public class ApiHttpAsyncClient
extends Object
implements HttpAsyncClient, Closeable
    An asynchronous HTTP client used in API connections. It is configured in a way suitable for communicating with XMS and is therefore most applicable for communicating with a single HTTP host.

    It is in most cases sufficient to let ApiConnection create and manage the HTTP client. If necessary, however, it is possible to create and manage this type of connections manually.
